There was one other sighting in Lakewood on or around November 22nd 2009
divs: Sighting DetailsI am reporting this sighting for the witness who called into Mufon Dispatch. Lisa Behr Witness was out hanging Christmas lights when he noticed what at first he thought were geese flying in formation. There were at least 50 objects flying in a "V" shaped formation and glowing with a slight greenish tint. He stated that each object seemed to have a mind of its own, yet stayed in formation. The "V" flew directly over his house at a slow rate of speed and then just disappeard over the horizon.
